  "3170130": {
    "name": "苏军敢死队：1944",
    "steam_appid": 3170130,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170130/extras/333362775eb22e414beb2da5c8a52404.avif?t=1749246953\" width=616 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《苏军敢死队》是一款融合了潜行元素的等距视角即时战术游戏。1944 年秋，你将指挥一支苏联侦察小队潜入东普鲁士。你的任务是：在红军战略进攻前夕，收集情报并对敌军发动精确打击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将面临各种各样的任务和情况，比如悄无声息地渗透进敌人的据点，在开阔战斗中熟练地管理小队等。你不仅要完成目标，还必须在远离前线的敌后存活下来，利用有限的资源，躲避敌人的持续追击，并与“中心”保持联系。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170130/extras/a11502af573489e4adddf70350769f4b.avif?t=1749246953\" width=616 height=364 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这样的任务只有久经沙场的战士才能胜任。你的麾下有来自普斯科夫森林的游击队员、波罗的海舰队的海军陆战队队员、斯摩棱斯克的资深地下工作者、泰加林猎人兼狙击手，以及众多其他战士。他们每个人都拥有在战争中磨练出的独特技能，加入小队的动机也各不相同。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关键特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >下一代即时战术游戏，你的游戏风格将决定完成任务的方式：可以悄无声息地行动，也可以展开全面交火。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >运用秘密渗透、无声击杀、伪装成当地平民等潜行战术，在战斗前占据上风，或者设下致命埋伏。  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170130/extras/74000142a41f28d9a9c9680aa09801c9.poster.avif?t=1749246953\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170130/extras/74000142a41f28d9a9c9680aa09801c9.webm?t=1749246953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170130/extras/74000142a41f28d9a9c9680aa09801c9.mp4?t=1749246953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸在大规模即时战术战斗中，巧妙利用掩护、战术机动和各种武器，即使面对数量占优的敌人，你也能将他们击败。  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170130/extras/2edf88cdcf0deddbd86c51ca5a9e6cb2.poster.avif?t=1749246953\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170130/extras/2edf88cdcf0deddbd86c51ca5a9e6cb2.webm?t=1749246953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170130/extras/2edf88cdcf0deddbd86c51ca5a9e6cb2.mp4?t=1749246953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用战术暂停功能，让多名小队成员同步行动，从而悄无声息地消灭敌人，或者掌控混乱的战斗局势。  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170130/extras/ed95e153296ffff7244a9fb7a2796ec1.poster.avif?t=1749246953\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170130/extras/ed95e153296ffff7244a9fb7a2796ec1.webm?t=1749246953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170130/extras/ed95e153296ffff7244a9fb7a2796ec1.mp4?t=1749246953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验伟大的卫国战争尾声激动人心的戏剧性事件——1944 年秋，红军对德意志帝国核心地带发动决战前夕，在东普鲁士执行侦察和破坏任务。  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170130/extras/dc47e53068f4bf5bf04b1d98537e373a.avif?t=1749246953\" width=600 height=320 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敌人持续追击、当地支援缺乏、资源稀缺、严冬逼近……你必须在敌后存活下来。  </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将扮演米罗诺夫上尉，一支特种作战小队的指挥官。他正在斯摩棱斯克附近的营地接受战斗训练。跳伞降落至东普鲁士，到达集合点，与“中心”取得联系，然后开始你的首个任务：侦察“伊尔门霍斯特”设防区域。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与在东普鲁士执行任务的其他苏联侦察小队取得联系。通过在敌占区进行精确打击和破坏行动，支援红军的推进。躲避专门用来追捕破坏行动人员的特种小队，并获取必须不惜一切代价送回“本土” 的秘密情报。</p>",
